WEBVTT

1
00:00:09.566 --> 00:00:12.900
I heard that the Empress Dowager visited you today.

2
00:00:13.400 --> 00:00:15.100
The Empress Dowager cares about me.

3
00:00:15.300 --> 00:00:17.233
She brought me many things.

4
00:00:17.766 --> 00:00:19.433
Could it be that someone is listening through the walls?

5
00:00:19.866 --> 00:00:21.933
If the Emperor finds out I’m scheming with the Empress Dowager,

6
00:00:21.933 --> 00:00:23.100
it concerns the Consort's matter.

7
00:00:23.566 --> 00:00:26.266
I don’t want to hurt the Empress Dowager’s feelings.

8
00:00:26.266 --> 00:00:29.300
In the future, you should accompany the Empress Dowager more for me.

9
00:00:29.733 --> 00:00:31.833
The Empress Dowager treats me very well.

10
00:00:31.933 --> 00:00:33.700
Even if the Emperor doesn’t mention it,

11
00:00:33.866 --> 00:00:36.466
I will still show great respect to the Empress Dowager.

12
00:00:37.500 --> 00:00:38.500
By the way,

13
00:00:38.500 --> 00:00:40.300
Although the Emperor has disagreements with the Empress Dowager,

14
00:00:40.300 --> 00:00:41.466
he is still quite filial.

15
00:00:41.766 --> 00:00:43.266
With the Empress Dowager’s support,

16
00:00:43.733 --> 00:00:45.300
I should be able to escape unscathed.

17
00:00:45.300 --> 00:00:47.700
I know you are a kind person.

18
00:00:47.966 --> 00:00:49.800
Is it just my impression,

19
00:00:50.500 --> 00:00:52.200
but since the selection yesterday,

20
00:00:52.200 --> 00:00:53.400
why does it feel like the Emperor

21
00:00:53.400 --> 00:00:55.700
has become a completely different person?

22
00:00:55.700 --> 00:00:59.533
Manager Li, bring the chosen ones.

23
00:00:59.533 --> 00:01:01.133
Tomorrow is Consort Feng's coronation.

24
00:01:01.133 --> 00:01:03.633
These are the maids I specially selected for you.

25
00:01:03.800 --> 00:01:06.433
See if you are satisfied.

26
00:01:06.600 --> 00:01:09.700
This maid is not only skilled but also very capable.

27
00:01:09.700 --> 00:01:11.033
She is a suitable head maid.

28
00:01:11.100 --> 00:01:13.966
To have such a person as my head maid is a waste.

29
00:01:13.966 --> 00:01:15.166
But the Emperor is monitoring me.

30
00:01:15.166 --> 00:01:16.700
He’s actually going this far.

31
00:01:19.066 --> 00:01:22.433
This young lady is very graceful and delicate.

32
00:01:22.566 --> 00:01:24.066
It’s a waste for her to be my maid.

33
00:01:24.133 --> 00:01:25.400
No, no, that won’t do.

34
00:01:25.400 --> 00:01:26.466
Ah.

35
00:01:28.066 --> 00:01:28.900
Ah.

36
00:01:29.500 --> 00:01:30.866
You deserve the best.

37
00:01:31.866 --> 00:01:32.966
Yes.

38
00:01:32.966 --> 00:01:34.966
From now on, protect the Consort well for me.

39
00:01:34.966 --> 00:01:36.700
If anything happens to her,

40
00:01:36.700 --> 00:01:38.166
you will be held accountable.

41
00:01:38.600 --> 00:01:39.700
I understand.

42
00:01:40.300 --> 00:01:41.233
Ah.

43
00:01:42.933 --> 00:01:44.566
Greet Consort Rong.

44
00:01:45.966 --> 00:01:46.766
Ah.

45
00:01:47.700 --> 00:01:49.866
Please rise, young lady.

46
00:01:50.100 --> 00:01:52.833
I will rely on you in the future. Thank you, Consort.

47
00:01:53.066 --> 00:01:55.566
I wonder if the Empress Dowager can change her mind.

48
00:01:55.566 --> 00:01:57.566
With such a head maid by my side,

49
00:01:57.566 --> 00:01:59.266
I fear I might be doomed before I can call for Consort Yang.

50
00:01:59.266 --> 00:02:00.766
I might be done for.

51
00:02:00.766 --> 00:02:02.200
Having a protective measure,

52
00:02:02.800 --> 00:02:04.400
I feel somewhat relieved.

53
00:02:04.766 --> 00:02:06.166
In this life,

54
00:02:06.200 --> 00:02:08.666
I won’t let the Empress suffer any harm.
